</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_40" id="18v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_40_r2l31">Bẏſſchoff cʒu <expan>wırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_40_r2l32"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als vns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade nehſt <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvie</del> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l35">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdikeit in den oſterveyertagen ſchierſt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_40_line_1573630942077_281">wir etlıche des <expan>R<ex>eichs</ex></expan> Stet 
<del rend="strikethrough">her cʒu vns </del> ın den oſter feyer her ʒu vns <expan>ʒekume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> herauff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l37">
<del rend="strikethrough">gen <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> cʒureyten maint </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_40_r2l36">beſenden ſolten etc </ab></add> etc / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> ſenden wir cʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l39">
<del rend="strikethrough">gnaden </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_40_line_1573631197090_303"><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></ab></add> hanſen Mawrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener <expan>weiſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dicʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l40"><expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> dauon cʒu reden / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elbe</ex></expan> etc ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_40_r2l41"><expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıȷ̃ poſt dıem <expan>Palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_40" id="18v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade
                        nehst <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, daz <add>wir etliche des
                            <expan>r<ex>eichs</ex></expan> stet in den <app><note><q type="date">oster feyer</q>Der Ostersonntag fiel auf den 15.04.1408.</note></app> her zu
                            uns <expan>zekume<ex>n</ex></expan></add> herauff <add>besenden solten
                            etc.</add> etc. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> senden wir czu
                                    <add><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add> Hansen Mawrer,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener,
                            <expan>weis<ex>er</ex></expan> dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>, mit
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> davon czu reden und
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz <expan>ders<ex>elbe</ex></expan>
                        etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii post diem <expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
